title: Total War: Arena - Leonidas - #1 - My First look with Jackie Fish
description:
This is my first look at Total War Arena!  A fellow Total War Youtuber, Jackie Fish, joins me and helps guide me through the game!  I hope you don't mind that I am so focused on the game!  It was Really fun :D

Check out Jackie fish's awesome channel: https://www.youtube.com/user/Jackiefishhhhhh


Follow me on twitter: https://twitter.com/pixelatedapollo
How to send me battle replays: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=7nG3uZoDkCU
How to play Medieval 2 Online: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=YGfItCMitPg
